2. Want older: set since = t0 - 1 second? then we get 720 bars from t0-... Actually we want candles that END before t0.

Better approach: use since = very old epoch to get first 720 from history, then repeatedly request since = last_received_newest + 1 until we reach now. That paginates forward through history.

Algorithm forward pagination:
